description: Rational knots with n crossings (up to mirroring).
comments: Identical through a(13) = 352 with Two-bridge Knots of crossing number n, in Table 1: Number of knots having two-bridged Conway polynomials, of Koseleff.There is a conjecture that this is the same as A090596.

P. -V. Koseleff, D. Pecker, Conway polynomials of two-bridge links, arXiv:1011.5992 [math.GT], 2010.
